text: Sterling Siloe Yatéké (born 12 June 1999) is a Central African professional footballer who plays as a striker for HNK Rijeka in Croatia, on loan from Austrian Bundesliga side Austria Wien. ==References== ==External links== *TPS Profile Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Association football forwards Category:Central African Republic footballers Category:Turun Palloseura footballers Category:FK Austria Wien players Category:HNK Rijeka players Category:Veikkausliiga players Category:Austrian Football Bundesliga players Category:Croatian First Football League players Category:Central African Republic expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Finland Category:Expatriate footballers in Austria Category:Expatriate footballers in Croatia
